# Terraform
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfvars
!*.tfvars.example
crash.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
.terraformrc
terraform.rc

# Go / operator
operator/bin/
*.test
*.out

# Helm
charts/**/charts/
*.tgz

# OS / editor
.DS_Store
*.swp
mage_output_file.go

# Graphviz/diagram render byproducts (the committed .png is the artifact)
docs/architecture/diagrams/core
*.dot

# IAM policy artifacts are rendered at apply time (the .tf is the source of truth)
modules/aws/iam/artifacts/
# Terraform module lock files (modules don't pin; only root configs do)
modules/**/.terraform.lock.hcl

# Ephemeral standalone-EKS validation root (live resource IDs; not product code)

# Release build artifacts (packaged charts, SBOMs)
dist/

# Composition roots are consumer-owned scaffolding (reference compositions live in docs).
live/
